      <h2>Curriculum Vitae (English)</h2>
      <p><strong>Eng. Mohammad Samir Dames</strong> is a Syrian civil engineer with a Bachelor's degree from the University of Idlib (2020, GPA: 78.13). He has extensive experience in infrastructure, WASH, and shelter projects with organizations like Islamic Relief, Orange, Bahar, and IYD.</p>
      <p>He is proficient in AutoCAD, Revit, ETABS, SAP2000, SewerGEMS, Excel, Power BI, and MS Project. Certified trainer in structural design, documentation, and quantity surveying.</p>
